# Model preference – OpenAI only

- Use **OpenAI models only**. Do not use Claude or other Anthropic models.
- Do not require an Anthropic API key.
- Use the **OpenAI API key** configured in Cursor settings.
- Prefer **gpt-4.1** (or **gpt-5-mini** if available).
- If a model fails, fall back to another **OpenAI** model. Do not switch to Claude automatically.
